			<phrase strongs="1471">of the heathen</phrase>
			<phrase strongs="1986">have broken down</phrase>
			<phrase strongs="8291">the principal plants</phrase>
			<phrase strongs="5060">thereof, they are come</phrase>
			<phrase strongs="3270">even unto Jazer,</phrase>
			<phrase strongs="8582">they wandered</phrase>
